title: Dungeon breaker! Heroes
description: Dungeon breaker! Heroes http://speed-imagens.net/imagens/5d43925060.jpg Dungeon breaker! Heroes - lead a team of brave heroes and go to find the queen, kidnapped by evil monsters. Destroy all enemies on the way. Join monster hunters in this Android game. Take your squad across dark dungeons, fight against enemies and gather loots. Defeat powerful bosses and complete daily tasks. Buy excellent weapons and outfit for your heroes. Level up your favorite characters and raise their characteristics. Test your team in the arena battles against players from all over the world
